i-MSCP RemoteBridge plugin ChangeLog
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.6
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Added: Get all i-MSCP accounts
		- action 'check_mail'
	- Added: Update an existing i-MSCP account
		- action 'delete_mail'
	- Fix: Bugs and missing arrays in function addMailAccount()
	- Fix: Some CS
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Added: Get all i-MSCP accounts
		- action 'get_users'
	- Added: Update an existing i-MSCP account
		- action 'update_user'
	- Added: Get all mail accounts of an existing i-MSCP account
		- action 'get_mails'
	- Added: Add a new mail account to an existing i-MSCP account
		- action 'add_mail'

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Fixed: Disabled items must not be counted by the getCountRequests() method
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Fixed: Column domain_created_id has been removed from i-MSCP core

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Small fixes

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2013-11-18: Sascha Bay
	- RELEASE i-MSCP RemoteBridge plugin 0.0.1
